Interface FlowImplementation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AObject, ClassifierFeature, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, Flow, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, ModalElement, ModalPath, NamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FlowImplementationImpl

    public interface FlowImplementation
extends ModalPath, ClassifierFeature, Flow
    A representation of the model object 'Flow Implementation'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Kind
    • Specification
    • Owned Flow Segment
